{"tid":1779381,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《時代》周刊風雲人物網民票選，「香港示威者」獲得超過30%網民支持，大幅拋離第2位","createTime":"2019-12-11T15:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T16:16:05.000Z","uid":43939,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"318cada4e970c41a12ab3ecd936ae59c94333652","tid":1779381,"uid":43939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T15:29:59.000Z","msg":"《時代》周刊風雲人物網民票選，於香港時間周二凌晨截止投票，《時代》公佈本年度逾2700萬人投票，結果「香港示威者」獲得超過30%網民支持，大幅拋離第2位、超過4.5%網民投票的，第2至第5位分別是「氣候示威者」（The Climate Strikers），第3至第5位分別是主演《殺神John Wick 3》的荷李活男星奇洛李維斯（Keanu Reeves）、去年票王南韓「防彈少年團」BTS及通貝里。<br />\n<br />\nSources : <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TIME/status/1204774056291110912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTIME%2Fstatus%2F1204774056291110912&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnACIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=864b0e35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTIME%2Fstatus%2F1204774056291110912&h=460963f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TIME/status/1204774056291110912</a><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，而家TIMES呢個支線任係百利而無一，幫手繼續係TWITTER 吹大佢唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39edf7e5fa333b02553add2b6545dfa04b8e9e48","tid":1779381,"uid":253978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T15:31:02.000Z","msg":"靜靜哋贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉"},{"pid":"afab3233a317a67080968d2f70eccaeac22f960d","tid":1779381,"uid":43939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39edf7e5fa333b02553add2b6545dfa04b8e9e48","tid":1779381,"uid":253978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T15:31:02.000Z","msg":"靜靜哋贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T15:34:55.000Z","msg":"鼓勵下姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2e1cf589a2f92cf44b16cf3f7492ba9f5712b4","tid":1779381,"uid":295813,"l